data.meta_description: RPH-Quiz 1 - Prelim (1).rtf - Free download as (.rtf), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document appears to be a quiz on Philippine history. It contains multiple choice questions about topics like historical sources, Filipino history, Corazon Aquino's speech, and key figures like Magellan. The questions cover definitions of terms like primary sources, internal criticism, and travelogues. Events mentioned include Magellan's death in Mactan and Aquino's 1986 speech to the US Congress seven months into her presidency.
